      <li>Faster access (no browser required)</li>
    </ul>
    <p><strong>Best apps:</strong> AuroraMe, My Aurora Forecast, Glendale</p>

    <h3>Websites</h3>
    <p><strong>Advantages:</strong></p>
    <ul>
      <li>More detailed technical data (NOAA)</li>
      <li>Larger maps and charts</li>
      <li>No app storage required</li>
    </ul>
    <p><strong>Best websites:</strong> NOAA SWPC, AuroraWatch, Soft Serve News</p>

    <p>
      <strong>Recommendation:</strong> Use both. Install a mobile app for alerts, bookmark NOAA website for verification when major storms are predicted.
    </p>
